      • MalmoEnv

        public MalmoEnv(java.lang.String missionFileName,
                MalmoActionSpace actionSpace,
                MalmoObservationSpace observationSpace,
                org.deeplearning4j.malmo.MalmoObservationPolicy framePolicy,
                java.lang.String... clientPool)
        Create a MalmoEnv using a XML-file mission description and minimal set of parameters. Equivalent to MalmoEnv( loadMissionXML( missionFileName ), missionRecord, actionSpace, observationSpace, framePolicy, clientPool )
        Parameters:
        missionFileName - Name of XML file describing mission
        actionSpace - Malmo action space implementation
        observationSpace - Malmo observation space implementation
        framePolicy - Malmo frame policy implementation
        clientPool - Malmo client pool in host:port string form. If set to null, will default to a single Malmo client at 127.0.0.1:10000

        framePolicy - Malmo frame policy implementation
        clientPool - Malmo client pool; cannot be null
